  "name": "RPlog_Surprise_Gastus_Went_Boom",
  "title": "Another Death Star",
  "summary": "Aboard the NRSC Deliverance, New Republic leaders convene an emergency briefing after a new, fully operational Death Star, commanded by Emperor Valak, has destroyed the planet Gastus before their eyes. General Arands, still shaken from witnessing the attack, reports the catastrophe to Luke Skywalker, Leia, Han Solo, and Chewbacca, who had only just arrived from Corellia, while Captain Howie Darklighter tries to steady the stunned room. An embarrassed NRI officer admits intelligence had no warning, noting a half-dozen undercover operatives have vanished in Imperial territory. With the captured Moff Morganna Tazecks held in the brig and no plans for the new station available, the leaders debate how to face a complete Death Star without the intelligence or plans they relied on before. Leia takes command, urging aggressive intelligence-gathering, border security, and warning all member worlds, while the junior diplomat Eva Sargent offers her CDU military contacts and Han and Chewbacca vow to find and destroy the station as they have twice before. Exhausted, the group resolves to rest, keep Morganna secured, and regroup once field agents report back, naming the NRI officer Diggs as their liaison.",
